{"number":15,"verseCount":6,"verses":[[1,["Hearken, my servant John, and listen to the words of Jesus Christ, your Lord and your Redeemer."]],[2,["For behold, I speak unto you with ",["sharpness",["study-note-ref","a",[["Hel. 3:29 (29–30)","bofm/hel/3.29"],". ",["TG God, Power of","tg/god-power-of"],"."]]]," and with power, for mine arm is over all the ",["earth",["study-note-ref","b",[["Ex. 9:29","ot/ex/9.29"],"; ",["D&C 14:9","dc-testament/dc/14.9"],"; ",["Abr. 4:12 (12, 24–25)","pgp/abr/4.12"],"."]]],"."]],[3,["And I will ",["tell",["study-note-ref","a",[["TG God, Omniscience of","tg/god-omniscience-of"],"."]]]," you that which no man ",["knoweth",["study-note-ref","b",[["D&C 6:16","dc-testament/dc/6.16"],"."]]]," save me and thee alone—"]],[4,["For many times you have desired of me to know that which would be of the most worth unto you."]],[5,["Behold, blessed are you for this thing, and for speaking my words which I have given you according to my commandments."]],[6,["And now, behold, I say unto you, that the thing which will be of the most worth unto you will be to ",["declare",["study-note-ref","a",[["D&C 6:6","dc-testament/dc/6.6"],"; ",["18:15 (15–16)","dc-testament/dc/18.15"],"; ",["30:9 (9–10)","dc-testament/dc/30.9"],"."]]]," ",["repentance",["study-note-ref","b",[["TG Missionary Work","tg/missionary-work"],"; ",["Repent","tg/repent"],"."]]]," unto this people, that you may bring ",["souls",["study-note-ref","c",[["TG Conversion","tg/conversion"],"; ",["Soul","tg/soul"],"; ",["Worth of Souls","tg/worth-of-souls"],"."]]]," unto me, that you may ",["rest",["study-note-ref","d",[["TG Rest","tg/rest"],"."]]]," with them in the ",["kingdom",["study-note-ref","e",[["TG Kingdom of God, in Heaven","tg/kingdom-of-god-in-heaven"],"."]]]," of my ",["Father",["study-note-ref","f",[["TG God the Father, Elohim","tg/god-the-father-elohim"],"."]]],". Amen."]]],"volume":"dc"}